<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Bantaeng Digital Map</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #1a1a24;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #00d2d3;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            color: #a4b0be;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Container Utama Map */
        .map-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Kartu Lokasi */
        .location-card {
            position: relative;
            background: #2f3542;
            width: 300px;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border: 2px solid #57606f;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease, border-color 0.4s ease;
        }

        /* Animasi saat kartu disentuh/di-hover */
        .location-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: #00d2d3;
        }

        /* Tampilan Default (Nama Lokasi / Peta Buta) */
        .location-default {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 2;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #341f97 0%, #2f3542 100%);
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .location-default .pin-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        .location-default h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Konten Tersembunyi (Foto & Info) */
        .location-info {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.9);
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        /* Foto Background */
        .location-info img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* Overlay Teks di atas Foto */
        .info-overlay {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95) 40%);
            padding: 20px;
            padding-top: 60px;
        }

        .info-overlay h3 {
            color: #00d2d3;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .info-overlay p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #f1f2f6;
        }

        /* REAKSI SAAT HOVER / TOUCH */
        /* Menyembunyikan nama lokasi default */
        .location-card:hover .location-default,
        .location-card:active .location-default {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(1.1);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Menampilkan foto dan info tersembunyi */
        .location-card:hover .location-info,
        .location-card:active .location-info {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1);
            z-index: 3;
        }

        /* Animasi Pin Bergerak */
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        /* Responsif untuk Layar HP */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .map-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>The Bantaeng Digital Map</h1>
        <p>Arahkan kursor atau sentuh lokasi untuk membuka rahasia keindahannya</p>
    </header>

    <div class="map-container">

        <div class="location-card" tabindex="0">
            <div class="location-default">
                <div class="pin-icon">📍</div>
                <h2>Seruni</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="location-info">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Pantai Seruni">
                <div class="info-overlay">
                    <h3>Pantai Seruni</h3>
                    <p>Ikon area publik di Bantaeng. Pusat kuliner, olahraga, dan tempat terbaik menikmati pemandangan matahari terbenam di tepi laut.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="location-card" tabindex="0">
            <div class="location-default">
                <div class="pin-icon">📍</div>
                <h2>Eremerasa</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="location-info">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504280390367-361c6d9f38f4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Permandian Eremerasa">
                <div class="info-overlay">
                    <h3>Eremerasa (Erma)</h3>
                    <p>Mata air alami yang sangat sejuk dan jernih di tengah rimbunnya pepohonan purba. Tempat paling menyegarkan untuk melepas penat.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="location-card" tabindex="0">
            <div class="location-default">
                <div class="pin-icon">📍</div>
                <h2>Loka</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="location-info">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Agrowisata Loka">
                <div class="info-overlay">
                    <h3>Agrowisata Loka</h3>
                    <p>Terletak di dataran tinggi pegunungan Bantaeng. Menawarkan udara yang dingin, pemandangan indah, serta agrowisata stroberi dan sayuran segar.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
